description: The same tasty charbroiled burgers and feel-good ambience from the TK restaurants that everyone in the OC knows and loves, can now be brought straight to your turf, thanks to these big ole festive TK Burger trucks. Whether you’re planning a small gathering or a huge corporate event, invite TK’s to come surf up and serve up their delicious burgers, fries, and cool beachy vibes. Your guests will be absolutely delighted to dive right into these fresh, made-to-order meals. When it comes to providing the best food and fun, TK Burgers definitely takes the cake.
name: TK Burgers
